晨報.definition: morning newspaper; (in a newspaper's name) Morning Post

晨昏.definition: morning and twilight; day and night

晨昏定省.definition: morning and evening visits to parents; cf 昏定晨省[hun1 ding4 chen2 xing3]

晨曦.definition: first rays of morning sun; first glimmer of dawn

晨鐘暮鼓.definition: lit. morning bell, evening drum, symbolizing monastic practice (idiom); fig. encouragement to study or progress
